Sweep 1.4.5

Dependencies:
    python
    python-chardet
    
Examples:

Connect on irc.freenode.net with nick Doritao, and join in ##null channel
./sweep -network:irc.freenode.net -nick:Doritao -join:##null -log:sessoes/freenode.txt

Connect on MSN (to configure you need to open the file ./modulos/msn.py and edit)
./sweep -msn -log:sessoes/msn.txt

The show the input/output messages
./sweep -network:irc.freenode.net -debug


Oh, you can configure the bot, editing the config.py file :)
